channel.title: Showing off my Edited auto staff application sender :P
channel.description:
I would first like to say This is kinda useless but i have also been told it was pretty cool and have made a few of these for my friends servers.
This was written in VB Scribt. What it does is keyloggs what you right in the Text box below then when pushing send. It will send it to my Email. Self explanitory?
Time it took to make: 1 day I had fun making it :P
[b]I will make anyone one of these if they want[/b] all i have to do is change the email address in the code not hard so pm me or leave a comment below if you want one of these for your server :)

item.title: Showing off my Edited auto staff application sender :P
item.dc:creator: @PlucScape PlucScape
item.description:
@PlucScape wrote:

[quote=“locksmin, post:3, topic:378716”][quote author=Davidi2 link=topic=474576.msg3470146#msg3470146 date=1295225960]

What it does is keyloggs what you right
[/quote]Hmmmm

Anyways, if it only works for your email, what is the point of this?

It only keyloggs what you right into the box lol not your whole computer you can get a .exe compiler and check for your self if you dont beleive me

And if someone doesn’t have forums for there server i guess you could use this? The big point of this is. is that i enjoyed making it lol and wanted to show it off.

I also want to expand it some how which is also why i kinda posted it on here for some ideas people could give me?

I also stated i will give this to people for there server’s if they want. all i would have to do is change the email address in the code.[/quote]

Let me call that inexperience.
It does NOT keylog at all.
All there is to it is a textbox, a button, some layers and a progressbar. It’s rather the most basic program you can make.
I don’t see what is the big deal in this. Without offense, I don’t think it’s worth working on from the beginning, so I advice you stop right there until you simply waste your time.

Also you could just make a “::suggest” type of form IN the server if you see what I mean.

And again I am shocked you claim it to KEYLOG…
Man, what a drag…
Anyhow let’s not start a big argument about it.
[center]These articles could enlighten you, I suppose.
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Keylogger
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Textbox [/center]

Anyways, nice try.
